# Bank Project

A simple banking application built with Flask to demonstrate debit and credit operations. The application has a background image and a user-friendly interface.

## Features

- Choose between **Debit** and **Credit** operations.
- Enter the amount to perform the transaction.
- A background image to enhance visual appeal.

## Technologies Used

- **Python**: Backend logic.
- **Flask**: Web framework.
- **HTML & CSS**: Frontend design.

